## Common Mistakes to Avoid

1. ❌ Too much implementation detail (specific CSS values instead of principles)
2. ❌ Missing design philosophy section
3. ❌ No accessibility checklist (WCAG compliance required)
4. ❌ Incomplete component checklist (missing common components)
5. ❌ No dark mode consideration
6. ❌ Missing responsive design principles
7. ❌ Not using checklist format consistently
8. ❌ Too long (> 300 lines) - should be focused on principles
9. ❌ Framework-specific when should be universal
10. ❌ No design token guidance

